#: ../../accessibility.rst:4
msgid ""
"This website is hosted and maintained by `Astun Technology "
"<https://astuntechnology.com/>`__ on behalf of the `Natural Resources "
"Wales <https://naturalresources.wales/>`__. We want `Natural Resources "
"Wales Metadata <https://metadata.naturalresources.wales/>`__ to be "
"accessible and usable for as many people as possible."
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:7
msgid "How accessible this website is"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:9
msgid "We know some parts of this website are not fully accessible:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:11
msgid ""
"Not all non-text content is available in text form, for example not all "
"images have \"alt\" attributes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:12
msgid "Not all content can be rendered using assistive technology"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:13
msgid "Some elements such as links are distinguishable only by colour"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:14
msgid ""
"Not all pages have titles or descriptions that adequately describe their "
"purpose"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:15
msgid "Not all links have a purpose that can be determined by the link text alone"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:16
msgid ""
"Entering data into controls does not always have a predictable effect, "
"nor are consistent instructions provided on their use"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:20
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:22
msgid ""
"If you cannot access any part of this site or want to report an "
"accessibility problem, please  `tell us "
"<mailto:opendata@cyfoethnaturiolcymru.gov.uk>`__."
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:24
msgid ""
"`AbilityNet <https://mcmw.abilitynet.org.uk/>`__ has advice on making "
"your device easier to use if you have a disability."
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:28
msgid "Enforcement procedure"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:30
msgid ""
"The Equality and Human Rights Commission enforces the `accessibility "
"regulations "
"<http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2018/952/regulation/4/made>`__ (the "
"Public Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile Applications) (No. 2) "
"Accessibility Regulations 2018)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:32
msgid ""
"If you're not happy with how we respond to your feedback, `contact the "
"Equality Advisory and Support Service "
"<https://www.equalityadvisoryservice.com/>`__. They are an independent "
"advice service. They will advise you on what to do next."
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:35
msgid "Compliance statement"
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:37
msgid ""
"Natural resources Wales commits to making its websites accessible, in "
"accordance with the Public Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile "
"Applications) (No. 2) Accessibility Regulations 2018. This accessibility "
"statement applies to `Natural Resources Wales Metadata "
"<https://metadata.naturalresources.wales/>`__ and was last reviewed on 7 "
"March 2024."
msgstr ""

#: ../../accessibility.rst:39
msgid ""
"The site was reviewed using the SiteImprove Chrome plugin in August 2020."
